    "title": "京东开放平台商品信息与实物不符细则",
    "followRuleId": "1241929979575537664",
    "content": "<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【违规定义】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">样式不符：指商家在商品的宣传中，提供的商品信息（如款式、颜色、图案、形状等）与实际商品存在明显差异的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规格参数不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供与实际商品不符的规格或参数信息的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">材质不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供与实际商品材质不符的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">产地不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，商品产地与商品实际情况不符的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.5</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">品种不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，商品品种与商品实际情况不符的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.6</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">重量不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供与实际商品重量不符的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.7</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">虚拟商品与实际应用不符：指商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供商品实际应用与宣传不符的的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.8</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">滥用随机发货声明：指商家商品主图/标题/名称/详情页等位置标明&ldquo;随机发货&rdquo;字样，但存在以下误导/欺骗消费者行为</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1）随机发货信息展示不一致，即商品为随机发货商品，但商品主图/标题/名称/详情页等多位置展示为单一商品，误导消费者下单并引起消费者投诉，视为滥用随机发货声明信息；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2）标注随机发货商品但实际非同款商品，即随机发货范围内商品品牌、功能、用途等发生明显变化，或因材质、构造变化而导致商品价值、质量发生变化，视为滥用随机发货声明范围。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3）随机发货页面发布规则详见：<a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: underline; color: #0563c1; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1303342051379920896\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: black;\">https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1303342051379920896</span></a> </span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 3; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度轻微：预警整改，整改失败/超期未整改下架违规商品；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 3; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度一般：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品近14天成交金额的10%，最低100元，最高10,000元）（M3档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 3; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品近14天成交金额的20%，最低300元，最高100,000元）（M4档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 3; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、扣除违约金（违规商品近14天成交金额的30%，最低500元，最高500,000元）（M5档）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; text-align: left; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家及其关联商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 2; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台根据违规行为对用户体验造成的伤害程度，从轻到重执行M1到M7档位违约金，具体金额如下：</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.2pt; background: #dc1623; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.2pt; background: #dc1623; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">用户体验伤害分级</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 367.7pt; background: #dc1623; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金标准</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M1</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害一级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 367.7pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">元及以下</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M2</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害二级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 367.7pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">固定金额 200元/500元/800元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害三级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 367.7pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">「违规商品/商家/门店」近14天成交金额10%，最低100元，最高10,000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M4</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害四级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 367.7pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">「违规商品/商家/门店」近14天成交金额20%，最低300元，最高100,000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M5</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害五级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 367.7pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">「违规商品/商家/门店」近14天成交金额30%， 最低500元，最高500,000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 48.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M6</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.2pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-f