 line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违规类型</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.85pt; background: #c00000; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违规定义</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 246.05pt; background: #c00000; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"328\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违规情形</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50.3pt; background: #c00000; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"67\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 69.9pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"93\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">样式不符</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.85pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在商品的宣传中，提供的商品信息（如款式、颜色、图案、形状等）与实际商品存在明显差异的行为。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 246.05pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"328\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-famil