ont-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3-M5</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 69.9pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"93\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">产地不符</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.85pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在宣传或销售商品时，商品产地与商品实际情况不符的行为。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 246.05pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"328\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）将国产宣传为进口；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）将普通大闸蟹宣传为阳澄湖大闸蟹等。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50.3pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"67\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3-M5</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 69.9pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"93\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">品种不符</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.85pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在宣传或销售商品时，商品品种与商品实际情况不符的行为。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 246.05pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"328\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）宣传金枕榴莲，实际商品为甲仑榴莲；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）宣传孔雀鱼苗，实际普通鱼苗。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50.3pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"67\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3-M5</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 69.9pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"93\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">重量不符</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.85pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供与实际商品重量不符的行为。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 246.05pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"328\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）商家宣传商品重量为&ldquo;5kg&rdquo;，而实际商品重量为&ldquo;1kg&rdquo;；</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50.3pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"67\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3-M5</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 69.9pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"93\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">虚拟商品与实际应用不符</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.85pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在宣传或销售商品时，提供商品实际应用与宣传不符的的行为。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 246.05pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"328\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）宣传19元180G流量，实际只有80G；</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50.3pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"67\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3-M5</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 69.9pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"93\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">滥用随机发货声明</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148.85pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"198\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家商品主图/标题/名称/详情页等位置标明&ldquo;随机发货&rdquo;字样，但存在以下误导/欺骗消费者行为</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 246.05pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"328\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">具体参考</span><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1303342051379920896\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1303342051379920896</span></a></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 50.3pt; padding: 0.75pt; line-height: 3;\" width=\"67\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M3-M5</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【附则】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家的行为，发生在本规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东可根据运营情况随时调整本管理规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.3</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有约定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无约定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议；若商家服务协议约定的违约金金额高于规则约定的，京东有权适用协议约定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.4</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本规则于2026年3月31日修订，于2026年4月8日生效。</span></span></p>",
